# Motor And Battery Setup

The selected setup is:

| Component | Selection        |
| --------- | ---------------- |
| Motors    | 2207 1750KV      |
| Props     | 5 inch tri-blade |
| Battery   | 4S 1500mAh LiPo  |

This setup gives:

* stable flying
* enough freestyle power
* manageable control for beginners

6S batteries were avoided because:

* more aggressive power
* harder tuning
* less beginner-friendly

4S is safer for learning.

