# NRF24 Communication System

The transmitter and receiver use:

## NRF24L01+ PA LNA modules

The PA LNA version was selected because:

* stronger signal
* external antenna
* better range
* more stable communication

One important thing discovered during research:
NRF24 modules are sensitive to unstable power.

Because of this:

## capacitors must be added.

A:

* 10uF
  or
* 47uF capacitor

is connected between:

* VCC
* GND

near the NRF24 module.

Without this capacitor:

* random disconnects
* unstable signals
* communication failure

can happen.

This is one of the most common mistakes in NRF24 projects.

